{"code": 0, "message": "OK", "ttl": 1, "data": {"list": {"slist": [], "tlist": {"155": {"tid": 155, "count": 1, "name": "时尚"}, "160": {"tid": 160, "count": 3, "name": "生活"}, "202": {"tid": 202, "count": 2, "name": "资讯"}, "211": {"tid": 211, "count": 6, "name": "美食"}, "217": {"tid": 217, "count": 335, "name": "动物圈"}}, "vlist": [{"comment": 1803, "typeid": 218, "play": 629244, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/ecf5400674a9a2af50747669d06ce00a1962713a.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "这期和大家讲了好多心里话\n其实我也没有你们想的那样坚强和勇敢\n我也会有敏感脆弱的时候\n也会有逃避和放弃的时候\n也会有控制不住自己情绪的时候\n但是好在我有一个积极的心态\n不管遇到什么\n我都会努力积极的去面对\n过去的事情就让他过去吧\n未来的生活，我会好好过\n即使有一天猫咪们会慢慢老去离开我\n但是它们曾经来过我的生命里\n留下了很多美好的回忆\n这就很够了！\n退一万步说，现在它们还好好地活着\n没准儿还能创造记录\n成为史上最长寿猫咪呢哈哈哈\n所以我们都要珍惜眼下\n过好每一天呀~", "copyright": "1", "title": "30岁了，我的猫也老了【花花与三猫】", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1765944000, "length": "07:44", "video_review": 699, "aid": 115729168997094, "bvid": "BV1zUqYBJEwu", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16768, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 394, "typeid": 218, "play": 301556, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/e668b0173f30c88eca38392642d52b3f02b4c17c.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "家人们，养女儿就是好啊！！\n女儿又香又软又可爱又文静！\njiojio小小的\n尾巴短短的\n叫声甜甜的\n文文静静的\n实在是太喜欢泡芙了！\n真的不能把泡芙送给我养吗？\n@香香软软的小泡芙  \n（当然不是说儿子不好的意思）\n主要是家里全是臭小子\n每天在家上蹿下跳，鸡飞狗跳，心惊肉跳\n难得体验一下养女儿的快乐哈哈哈\n那你们喜欢这期内容吗？\n还想看我去谁家交换呢？", "copyright": "1", "title": "百大萌宠《变形记》，三猫VS泡芙交换猫咪挑战！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1763780400, "length": "12:02", "video_review": 608, "aid": 115586981960980, "bvid": "BV1jtUVBHEEi", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 1, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16793984, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 417, "typeid": 218, "play": 380886, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/cc816cf7d608cc0bdb6a3627fe937cbd397775ec.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "老母亲的碎碎念：\n这个视频拍的没觉得羞耻\n视频剪完之后觉得好丢脸好羞耻\n又怕视频没人看难过\n又怕视频有很多人看更丢脸了\n于是就在这种好丢脸好羞耻的矛盾中发了这期视频\nps：此视频已经屏蔽我所有亲戚", "copyright": "1", "title": "《技 能 猫 爬 架》咕咕版", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1761624000, "length": "05:02", "video_review": 353, "aid": 115445818462408, "bvid": "BV1aVsUzNEzi", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16768, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 388, "typeid": 218, "play": 1137705, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/f2522a823a358063e04a0f62780bed8a90b3a799.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "从小看到大的弟弟居然都谈恋爱了\n还背着我偷偷带女朋友来家里撸猫\n猫猫们也是吃上“狗粮”了hhh\n就是家长来的太不凑巧了\n看把孩子弄得多害羞呀~\n下次再正式邀请来家里好好撸猫！\n也希望大家喜欢这期视频呀~", "copyright": "1", "title": "18岁弟弟偷带女友来我家撸猫，一不小心“见家长”了？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1757932687, "length": "07:38", "video_review": 484, "aid": 115207766612133, "bvid": "BV1vopMzdEQw", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16768, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 456, "typeid": 218, "play": 864082, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/8deaf4877cce99331dacfbb4805602ddd6a8d32b.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "越来越觉得中分聪明了\n现在还知道反向来逗我了\n到底是谁在养谁啊哈哈哈\n而且我这么整蛊中分\n它都没有生气怎么回事\n太宠我了一点吧哈哈哈哈\n希望你们喜欢这期视频呀～\n要是喜欢记得点个赞～\n这对我真的很重要！！爱你们～", "copyright": "1", "title": "趁猫上厕所时，让猫砂盆跑起来，猫：这推背感！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1756094400, "length": "06:13", "video_review": 611, "aid": 115087037764791, "bvid": "BV1A4e4zJESM", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16768, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 278, "typeid": 218, "play": 286254, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/cab7af09478d77816611e82e8f46d7c51314da64.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "叮叮叮！走过路过别错过～\n三花村女仆咖啡厅开业啦～\n我们有最“敬业”的猫女仆哦～\n超级甜美软萌可爱！\n任摸任撸配合度高！\n还会表演独门才艺！\n先到先得，赶紧来撸猫吧～\n感谢@矮乐多Aliga  的友情出演\n以后多来三花村做客呀~\n开业大礼：撸猫附赠猫毛大衣一件！", "copyright": "1", "title": "猫仆VS女仆，到底谁的业务能力更强？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1754650732, "length": "06:14", "video_review": 473, "aid": 114992699480477, "bvid": "BV1Qqtmz6EWS", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16768, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 860, "typeid": 218, "play": 1718717, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/7835063aad74f60c2a60132a7d3fe0b5f9e80a29.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "“三花村终于迎来妹妹啦！\n但是为什么妹妹没有尾巴？\n也没有满身的毛毛呢？\n但是妹妹闻起来奶香奶香的！\n而且妹妹会喂猫条！太棒啦！\n喂？！妹妹怎么拉在家里啊？！\n那明明是我的地盘！\n那我也要尿在她的小床上！”\n以上，是白老师乱尿后的全部心理活动", "copyright": "1", "title": "五猫之家终于有妹妹了，但妹妹怎么不是猫？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1753174800, "length": "06:25", "video_review": 1181, "aid": 114894972130022, "bvid": "BV1PcgnzzEUT", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16768, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 601, "typeid": 218, "play": 1747443, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/9e66d3bfde07bdb0cac5c694b9c74b0b76fcadef.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "当我给猫买了一个比它大几倍的大饼\n猫猫们无从下口哈哈哈\n猪：救救咪，咪被大饼卡住了？！\n胆小的甫甫第一次如此受欢迎\n被猫猫们围着又闻又舔又咬\n脾气大的白老师被死对头包围\n又会如何冲出重围呢？\n漂亮欧式贵族糕糕\n带上大饼围脖尽情彰显“贵族范”\n一起开看看吧~", "copyright": "1", "title": "饼之大，咪一口吃不下！【花花与三猫】", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1749548319, "length": "06:03", "video_review": 968, "aid": 114658296075067, "bvid": "BV1RdTrzrEuw", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 439, "typeid": 218, "play": 1174050, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/da75acb65b41f55fe5517c3ba2cad8178206c235.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "在经过6个月的治疗之后\n糕糕的过敏症状终于有所好转\n但是因为过敏导致的并发症——猫藓\n还需要进一步的治疗\n所以剃毛是为了治疗猫藓而不是过敏哦\n当然为什么这个时候剃毛之前不剃\n是因为夏天来啦，就不怕糕糕会感冒了\n大家放心，我是糕糕的铲屎官\n这个世界上不会有比我更爱它的人了\n所以剃毛也是我结合医生的建议\n并且找了很干净卫生的宠物店\n最终才完成的这件事\n谢谢大家对糕糕的喜爱和关心哦\n我一定会照顾好它的！", "copyright": "1", "title": "猫咪剃毛归来，昔日兄弟看我像“行走的大鸡腿”", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1747908000, "length": "07:04", "video_review": 6789, "aid": 114545787933928, "bvid": "BV1ByJ6zVErW", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 875, "typeid": 218, "play": 564777, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/882ca4d7f5e2210702774a959f035fc8e475bdb5.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "Hello,大家好~这里是三猫和五只猫猫的3月vlog~\n咦，怎么一下子就到3月了哈哈哈\n那么3月是我们家的两只小短腿的生日月哦~\n除了过生日以外，三花村还发生了很多事情！\n比如那一晚甫甫和糕糕都喝醉了...（不是）\n还有天降横屎，家里被糟蹋的惨不忍睹！\n以及关于宠物和爱的这件事~\n所以，一起来看看吧~希望你们喜欢这期视频~\nps：6分26秒音乐来源：BV1nHRkYcEvY", "copyright": "1", "title": "在爱里长大的小猫是怎么样的？【花花与三猫】", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1745295318, "length": "09:41", "video_review": 1177, "aid": 114379659940492, "bvid": "BV1nB5Dz8EKX", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 292, "typeid": 218, "play": 275124, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/d3f48b9d85812f599462d98e01bdff5429b11b2b.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "嗨嗨嗨~我又来了，简单咕咕两句\n没想到又更新了，我都有点不敢相信\n久违的奇葩系列，好久没更这类视频了\n都说了四川人手一只熊猫，你们还不信\n这下都相信了吧hhh\n就是不知道这个恐龙猫猫有没有吓到你们呢\n小朋友请在大人陪同下观看哦~", "copyright": "1", "title": "【三花村生物鉴定】新型物种“鹰头猫”？", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1742812194, "length": "04:55", "video_review": 672, "aid": 114216921012445, "bvid": "BV1qToyYKEhC", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": {"id": 5132671, "title": "猫猫搞笑日常，不好笑不要三连", "cover": "https://archive.biliimg.com/bfs/archive/ff7a9cc5f2eb3a8024ca860e26dd6f4d0533d075.jpg", "mid": 9008159, "intro": "不好笑不要三连", "sign_state": 0, "attribute": 156, "stat": {"season_id": 5132671, "view": 869695, "danmaku": 1809, "reply": 1106, "favorite": 8457, "coin": 23661, "share": 1470, "like": 79648, "mtime": 1769758827, "vt": 0, "vv": 0}, "ep_count": 4, "first_aid": 114216921012445, "ptime": 1742812194, "ep_num": 4}, "is_avoided": 1, "season_id": 5132671, "attribute": 268451968, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 1730, "typeid": 218, "play": 930474, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/11bbd5dab7a0838de6c86fbc0ef93c0562d8c2f4.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "hello，大家好~这里是三猫\n看到标题是不是吓一跳哈哈哈\n原谅我标题党一下下~\n这个猫猫已经被医院的护士领养了哦\n以后应该还会在视频里看到它的\n这期视频就比较日常一些\n不知道大家会不会喜欢看\n喜欢的话给我点个赞吧~\n以后我就每个月都做一期日常视频~\n那我们下期视频再见哦！爱你们~", "copyright": "1", "title": "我的第6只猫！它实在是太可爱了！【花花与三猫】", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1742270400, "length": "08:39", "video_review": 1898, "aid": 114177410602665, "bvid": "BV16cXMYfEdw", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 879, "typeid": 218, "play": 1133472, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/c3e0a46b3da6c79c78e184a263dc310e1cd96dc4.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "大家好呀~\n非常感谢这次能来现场的各位云爹妈们~\n第一次带猫见大家，我也是超级紧张的！\n感觉有很多做的不够周到的地方\n还请大家多多见谅~\n下次我再好好的准备一下\n希望能给大家更好的摸猫体验呀~\n这次也感谢HBN的大力支持\n让我们一起发光发亮，迎接每一天吧~", "copyright": "1", "title": "网红猫第一次线下见粉丝，差点被撸秃？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1740140623, "length": "06:22", "video_review": 805, "aid": 114041750099205, "bvid": "BV1g7Afe7E9p", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 538, "typeid": 218, "play": 395516, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/476ccdea55a30700fcb28f9ef9fb7dde9fbc029a.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "又到了一年一度给猫做年夜饭的时候啦\n今年猫猫们到底有没有给面子呢？\n感觉今年过得好快呀，一眨眼就过去了\n大家今年过得怎么样呀？\n有没有实现年初定下的目标？\n有没有实现许下的愿望？\n有没有成为更好的自己呢？\n成长的过程很辛苦吧~摸摸头~\n新的一年！我们要打起精神！\n一起为了美好的明天加油吧！\n新年快乐呀~~~", "copyright": "1", "title": "一家人和猫一起吃年夜饭，猫：我想吃铲屎官那一桌！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1737969011, "length": "07:47", "video_review": 738, "aid": 113899395355323, "bvid": "BV1difUYUEjF", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": {"id": 5132716, "title": "一家人和猫一起吃年夜饭，猫：我想吃铲屎官那一桌！", "cover": "https://archive.biliimg.com/bfs/archive/476ccdea55a30700fcb28f9ef9fb7dde9fbc029a.jpg", "mid": 9008159, "intro": "", "sign_state": 0, "attribute": 156, "stat": {"season_id": 5132716, "view": 723990, "danmaku": 1203, "reply": 894, "favorite": 6694, "coin": 16193, "share": 941, "like": 41375, "mtime": 1769758441, "vt": 0, "vv": 0}, "ep_count": 2, "first_aid": 113899395355323, "ptime": 1737969011, "ep_num": 2}, "is_avoided": 1, "season_id": 5132716, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 305, "typeid": 252, "play": 400077, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/8257500b305a0361b5af04685bf229e8495ba6fc.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "-", "copyright": "1", "title": "cos改造“花花与三猫”来了！！！", "review": 0, "author": "矮乐多Aliga", "mid": 259333, "created": 1736417100, "length": "08:58", "video_review": 1096, "aid": 113792205785551, "bvid": "BV1HurYY3E9j", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 1, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": {"id": 1287157, "title": "COS改造", "cover": "https://archive.biliimg.com/bfs/archive/2f90c23e3012997c3af2d1b317316fea36ec3055.jpg", "mid": 259333, "intro": "报名请投邮箱a.liga@163.com\n标题格式【你的名称+想出角色名+年龄性别】\n内容需要附上你的素颜照片+你想出的Cos的服装（需要自备），还有你的一些个人介绍或者想cos的原因，并且附上联系的q号即可（ps：请不要发送压缩文件，照片请直接填在邮件文案里就好了，不然阅览很难）\n目前仅招募可以在广州地区拍摄的小伙伴，男女老少不限～能力有限所以会采取随机的形式去选下一位参加的小伙伴。\n很感谢大家信任我这个化妆新手给你们改造，我希望能做得越来越好，不辜负你们的期望！！！", "sign_state": 0, "attribute": 140, "stat": {"season_id": 1287157, "view": 23130242, "danmaku": 57637, "reply": 25407, "favorite": 165041, "coin": 198629, "share": 38208, "like": 1188467, "mtime": 1769759049, "vt": 0, "vv": 0}, "ep_count": 35, "first_aid": 114884637492658, "ptime": 1753445100, "ep_num": 35}, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 1287157, "attribute": 16793984, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 444, "typeid": 218, "play": 315206, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/3cdfd1373371d144ee8460c67b3f019e6fa6ba3d.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "没想到只是因为想带中分去掏耳屎\n竟然让中分肿成了大猪头\n最后还不得不把头发全剃了\n变成了鸡冠头。。。\n中分：11月请对我好一点（呜呜）\n好在最后有惊无险的度过了\n现在中分已经好的差不多了\n大家也不用太担心哦~\n不过难得有中分的黑历史嘿嘿嘿\n当然要记录啦哈哈哈哈\n老母亲补充：\n中分是对洗耳朵的那个油过敏\n医生说从来没有猫猫会对那个油过敏\n偏偏中分就过敏了\n这样小的概率居然被中分碰到了\n也真的是倒霉蛋了", "copyright": "1", "title": "猫猫王子变青蛙？竟是一颗耳屎造成的？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1731061025, "length": "05:20", "video_review": 981, "aid": 113446796399316, "bvid": "BV1qwDZYsEvy", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 703, "typeid": 218, "play": 914849, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/f64561432a429a5a2c6aec4d496c1c325e785877.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "铲屎官不做人啦！\n居然敢一口气洗五只猫\n猫咪气的破口大骂\n场面一度混乱！\n到底是铲屎官大获全胜\n还是猫咪们反抗成功呢？！\n让我们拭目以待吧！\n友情提示：非专业行为，不建议模仿！", "copyright": "1", "title": "洗猫大作战！挑战一口气洗五只猫！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1730004156, "length": "08:29", "video_review": 2159, "aid": 113377389122813, "bvid": "BV1dV1hYeE95", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 349, "typeid": 218, "play": 319946, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/25ec44d863fabe9794d40b4a39c8fbc55164b169.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "没有广告没有广告没有广告\n（重要事情说三遍）\n这次亚宠展见到很多云爹妈超级开心！\n没想到我当咕咕的这段日子\n三花村都有“咕勇者”联盟了\n甚至当面催更hhhh\n错了错了（立马滑跪）\n这次也给五只猫带回来了很多好东西~\n猫猫们超级开心的！\n猫猫开心，铲屎官就开心！\n当然见到你们也很开心\n明年再见呀~", "copyright": "1", "title": "啥家庭啊，一口气给五只猫花了10000元？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1728126708, "length": "07:22", "video_review": 548, "aid": 113254496015167, "bvid": "BV18Q1RYdEup", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 1270, "typeid": 218, "play": 525669, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/2a978563655d322615c293538db6e5095bb57687.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "今年中分8岁啦！！\n感觉时间过得好快呀\n想起第一次去领养中分的时候\n它很害怕躲在沙发底下不愿意跟我走\n最后只能把沙发搬走才抓住了它\n一路上一直喵喵叫\n到家之后很紧张不吃不喝\n回想起这些画面\n仿佛就在昨天\n时间总是这样\n在不经意之间悄悄流逝\n等你再回过头的时候\n发现一切离你那么近又那么远\n不过好在，它一直都在我身边~\n那么，就好好珍惜当下的每分每秒吧~", "copyright": "1", "title": "今天过生日，都进来给本喵贺寿！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1727711999, "length": "06:56", "video_review": 3761, "aid": 113226494776246, "bvid": "BV1iYx4exEBo", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 541, "typeid": 218, "play": 343268, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/5f325279306ad05c64a60dd8bf760fe58710e026.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "一年一度的体检又又又来了\n这次是猫猫们来广州之后第一次体检\n没想到猫猫们太出名了\n医院的医生护士们都认识它们哈哈哈\n猫猫们也还是一如既往的不配合（哭笑不得）\n好在是顺顺利利的完成了体检\n体检报告也已经出来了\n猫猫们身体没什么大问题\n而且糕糕的过敏现在有治疗方案了\n等之后我专门出个视频详细讲讲\n希望大家也要多多关注自己和宠物们的身体健康\n那么我们下期视频再见啦~~", "copyright": "1", "title": "带猫去看医生，猫咪拒不配合，急的都要开口说话了！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1725792575, "length": "05:41", "video_review": 759, "aid": 113101521358480, "bvid": "BV1w3pBe8EX8", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 1275, "typeid": 218, "play": 425455, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/a8a69a533ed83eda296b57c7f4d79870abbbbef2.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "又到了一年一度的见面日了呀～\n今年老母亲把积攒多年的猫胡须带出来了！\n听说小猫咪的胡须可以许愿哦～\n今年还是在上海新国际博览中心\n我是24号下午3点-4点在E5的主舞台\n4点-5点在C1馆A08 B站 展位～\n期待和你们的见面哦～", "copyright": "1", "title": "快从我的扫地机器人上下来！猫：我就不！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1724419513, "length": "05:43", "video_review": 1552, "aid": 1406675096, "bvid": "BV1Ar421N7PT", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 1040, "typeid": 218, "play": 518779, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/1d4bff450f27e5972f50f4cb4c4a9916b4a42678.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "一直很好奇猫猫们心里到底怎么想的\n于是请了宠物沟通师来家里解答\n想不到猫猫们的心里竟然有这么多小心思\n白老师石锤心眼多了哈哈哈哈\n中分一如既往的贴心好大儿\n猪猪居然把中分当小弟看待？\n糕糕说一开始想当小绿茶然后被哥哥们嫌弃了哈哈哈哈\n甫甫直接就拒绝沟通，还是胆子太小了\n不管猫猫们的这些想法是真是假\n大家就当图一乐，看着乐呵乐呵就好\n毕竟无论如何，它们都是我们的好宝宝呀~", "copyright": "1", "title": "请猫咪沟通师来家里，竟让猫和主人抱头痛哭？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1721470092, "length": "07:50", "video_review": 1194, "aid": 1656469153, "bvid": "BV13E421A7TY", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 2626, "typeid": 218, "play": 992477, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/e54bb30c5868b926630417589db8747da8a7632b.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "大家好呀~不好意思这次更新有点晚了\n虽然人和猫都搬来广州了\n但是现在工作还没稳定下来\n有很多杂七杂八的事情要处理\n我一个人有点忙不过来\n所以目前更新还不是很稳定\n希望各位云爹妈们见谅呀~\n更无奈的是！\n我一搬过来，隔壁就开始清水房装修\n过了半个月，我楼上又开始清水房装修了\n现在就是，每天我和猫都在被双重折磨（哭哭）\n总而言之，我会好好加油的！\n遇到困难解决困难！！！\n大家也要加油呀~~~", "copyright": "1", "title": "29岁女生独居养五只猫的一天，到底爽不爽？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1720353707, "length": "05:09", "video_review": 1535, "aid": 1056079826, "bvid": "BV1CH4y1w7Pf", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 1520, "typeid": 218, "play": 1141420, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/78495209953aa99139bfbb8ba363773085b306d7.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "猪猪小朋友的牙也是历经九九八十一难了\n本来以为只是个小问题\n没想到直接拔牙了\n现在是缺牙巴猪猪了哈哈哈\n希望大家在看得时候笑的小声点\n给孩子留点面子\n还好不影响孩子吃饭\n现在依旧是吃嘛嘛香~\n大家也要保护好自己的牙齿哦~\n希望大家也能吃嘛嘛香，身体棒棒！", "copyright": "1", "title": "被骗了？！千万网红短腿橘猫，竟然是个地包天！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1718446030, "length": "05:46", "video_review": 1459, "aid": 1155624462, "bvid": "BV1CZ421u7WU", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 4387, "typeid": 218, "play": 1119811, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/d039ae511fd1867b4d2b8217d8c7dbc6d17012b4.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "hello，大家好，这里是三猫~\n好久不见，甚是想念~\n我知道这次见面等的太久了\n真的非常抱歉，对不起（90度鞠躬）\n如视频所见，我带着猫猫跨越2000多公里搬家啦~\n成都很好，但是广州也很好\n这里有我的家人，我想离家里人更近一些\n现在过上了走路5分钟就能回家吃饭日子\n家里的饭饭真的很好吃很好吃~\n我每天都过得很开心很幸福\n猫猫也一样\n希望你们也一样\n今后我会恢复更新的\n希望大家今后也多多包容\n多多指教啦~", "copyright": "1", "title": "带着5只猫跨越2000公里搬家是种什么体验？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1717927341, "length": "06:11", "video_review": 2419, "aid": 1905726604, "bvid": "BV17S411N71X", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 2552, "typeid": 218, "play": 659474, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/7d16759735fb06598f25de2fcd017696ffc45341.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "Hello，大家好呀～这里是三猫！真的好久好久不见了！！！\n先给大家道歉！对不起！！！让大家久等了呜呜呜！！！\n这段时间真的发生了很多很多事情，等有空我再把这些事情慢慢告诉你们，反正每一天都过得充实！真的好久好久没有这么痛快的玩过，把之前没休息的时间全补回来，这一补就补了半年……\n感谢你们一直不离不弃的在等我们，感谢你们仍旧期待我们的回归，感谢你们仍然喜欢和支持我们！！！爱你们么么哒～\n那么，亲爱的三花村的云爹妈们，今后也请多多指教啦～", "copyright": "1", "title": "元宵吃汤圆，猫猫拜晚年！！！【元宵节vlog】", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1710585591, "length": "04:48", "video_review": 1596, "aid": 1551918903, "bvid": "BV1y1421D7vq", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 1059, "typeid": 218, "play": 804284, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/a4b22c74bdf6ad207d97b596bf5a9a620e494ed2.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "救助流浪动物是我们一直在坚持做的事情，我们真诚地希望每一位小动物都能够被善待，养了它就要不抛弃，不放弃！再次感谢诚实一口对保护流浪动物做出的贡献，也感谢爱之家为流浪动物们提供的温暖庇护所。希望全天下的小猫咪从出生开始，都能拥有一个温暖的家和一个爱自己的铲屎官～", "copyright": "1", "title": "一次性绝育50只猫？！三花村史上最多绝育纪录！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1695380400, "length": "06:37", "video_review": 952, "aid": 576258760, "bvid": "BV1Jz4y1V7ok", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 397, "typeid": 218, "play": 317508, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/6f9d085f3a585f3c2e127753bd8857e8109f2861.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "时隔许久，终于迎来花花与三猫吃播剧场第三集！请提前备好耳机哦~这次给猫咪们吃了多种肉肉，量大管饱，时长9分钟！因为想要营造睡觉前比较舒适的光线，所以拍摄时灯光比较暗，后期时就发现画质上也会有点糊，希望大家见谅（或许模糊一点点看一会儿就能马上睡着？（不是）），下次再拍类似视频我一定会注意这一点的！", "copyright": "1", "title": "沉浸式猫咪吃肉肉，这个声音太上头了！！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1694855019, "length": "09:25", "video_review": 723, "aid": 406051780, "bvid": "BV1LV411N7dU", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 279, "typeid": 218, "play": 494463, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/1d5d2d31c058e107d0d798c8481163a10a036e06.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "又是一年一度和大家见面的时候呀~这次见到了很多很多云爹妈！真的超级超级开心！谢谢大家来见我，也谢谢大家的礼物，更要谢谢大家一直以来的喜欢和支持！！！\n\n今年因为逛展回来就重感冒了，拍这期视频的时候鼻涕横流，说话也有点鼻音，可能我的状态就有点不太好，希望大家多多包涵！现在感冒已经痊愈了，大家不用担心！\n\n今年逛展看到了很多很棒的产品，可惜好多都是新品，没办法带回来，加上时间紧，最后有几个展厅都没有逛到，感觉错过了很多有趣的东西！下次一定要把时间留够好好逛个够！！！\n\n那么就一起期待下次见面吧！", "copyright": "1", "title": "给猫洗脚后，奶牛猫被迷得神魂颠倒，橘猫：你不要过来啊！？", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1693474007, "length": "04:04", "video_review": 558, "aid": 702960239, "bvid": "BV11m4y1T7rb", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 751, "typeid": 218, "play": 1046748, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/19a1229b6802d5f3e87851c9206d80be1ff43bd6.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "事实证明气味对猫咪识别同伴来说非常重要，洗澡之后白老师遭到了全家的各种凶凶（除了甫甫），可以说是报应来的很快了（老母亲偷笑），甫甫今年暂时就不洗啦，jiojio受伤了，等jiojio好了再洗吧", "copyright": "1", "title": "猫咪洗完澡之后，为何家里发出了“警报声”？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1692706900, "length": "04:51", "video_review": 1489, "aid": 317586788, "bvid": "BV1mP411p7BR", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 616, "typeid": 218, "play": 862721, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/e2287a274918496e5bde78669831c98b4e1e8f34.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "今年体检顺利结束了，又是健健康康的一年，随着体检次数的增多，我们家的体检经验也越来越丰富啦！这次体检也揭开了一个小秘密，那就是猪猪的肥胖秘密！还是加油减肥吧猪猪！", "copyright": "1", "title": "肥猫去医院做体检，肥胖的原因竟然是这个？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1691832445, "length": "05:32", "video_review": 874, "aid": 957245874, "bvid": "BV1ap4y1g7xJ", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 580, "typeid": 218, "play": 1391041, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/c968662cd652db63f326db446639b8f534fd4604.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "因为甫甫哥胆子比较小，原本想在家里处理伤口，让它自己痊愈，没想到伤势比我想的更严重，于是我们还是来到了医院，好在处理了伤口之后慢慢痊愈了，截止到视频发出的时候，甫甫哥jio指甲已经长了一丢丢了", "copyright": "1", "title": "大头男明星的jiojio受伤了，铲屎官心疼坏了！！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1690624399, "length": "04:18", "video_review": 819, "aid": 231553928, "bvid": "BV1L841127Wk", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 520, "typeid": 218, "play": 786229, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/ed3a4d842d1a61566b3e0f394e217001a3ba5980.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "这些猫零食平时卖的那么贵，我一看这自己也能做不是吗，说干就干，过程还是很顺利的，没想到，这自己做的还是不如买的香，还不如生的受欢迎", "copyright": "1", "title": "给猫自制鸭胸肉干，猫：我就吃亿口，就亿口！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1689997901, "length": "04:19", "video_review": 809, "aid": 998734878, "bvid": "BV1ax4y1d7Sk", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 268451968, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 670, "typeid": 218, "play": 885337, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/12853bdeb7c37424b9047a050eee67212f192543.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "臭臭联盟遭遇史上最大危机！在洗澡这件事上它们本来都是可以独挡一面的！（指一只猫就让铲屎官累个半死），现在居然要被铲屎官一网打尽，一石二猫，一洗到底了！铲屎官究竟能否完成这艰巨的任务呢！？", "copyright": "1", "title": "一次性洗两只猫？！铲屎官：我后悔了！猫：我更后悔！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1688811414, "length": "04:56", "video_review": 1891, "aid": 273148868, "bvid": "BV1RF411R7QL", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 591, "typeid": 218, "play": 911710, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/b3fd2ebc65ae2dc0e894f5f84060942706b715cc.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "花花的好朋友来成都玩，因为他俩关系比较好，经常连动作习惯都很像，于是我灵机一动，请他来出演假的老父亲哈哈哈！看看猫猫们能不能通过考验，找到真正的老父亲！", "copyright": "1", "title": "请男朋友的“双胞胎”弟弟来假扮他，猫咪会认出来吗？", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1687946091, "length": "06:13", "video_review": 1983, "aid": 445275869, "bvid": "BV1sj411S7pC", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 619, "typeid": 218, "play": 1289215, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/d08f9d1f019a90479dab048f6c00d5c7c4fb53fe.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "时隔两年，再度开战！左边是来自三花村的资深铲屎官，为了这次的对决，她做了完全的准备，不仅提前剪掉了对方的指甲，而且还穿上了三百六十度无死角的防护服，是本次比赛的一匹黑马！右边则是来自三花村的村霸，人称大黑耗子，是擂台上的常青树，连续多次击败对手，在浴室当中他说第一，没人敢说第二！到底鹿死谁手，即将揭晓！", "copyright": "1", "title": "原来是洗猫啊，我还以为世界大战呢？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1686997152, "length": "04:20", "video_review": 1159, "aid": 357450912, "bvid": "BV11X4y147wo", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 374, "typeid": 218, "play": 766205, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/a543cade114185f1fc5f95294c562fe785784fe6.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "别人家的小猫咪都能够勇敢冲破封锁，抵达心中的那个彼方，为何我们家的小猫咪只会原地摆烂，不思进取。期待是一层小小的保鲜膜，麻麻在这头，猫猫在那头。", "copyright": "1", "title": "都是保鲜膜挑战，为什么我的猫却不一样？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1686387185, "length": "03:36", "video_review": 691, "aid": 699627264, "bvid": "BV1nm4y1q7D7", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 292, "typeid": 218, "play": 434255, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/131abb70e7889ea3f47fc14ea9534e2c1e763735.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "在家里给每只猫猫量了一下三围，没想到猫和猫之间的差距这么大！猪猪身长居然和分哥腿长差不多！甫大头不愧为甫大头，头是真滴大！另外糕糕和猪猪的腿也太短啦！", "copyright": "1", "title": "为了拍多巴胺穿搭，猫猫们也是拼了，竟然公开了三围？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1685264510, "length": "04:26", "video_review": 670, "aid": 399185225, "bvid": "BV18o4y137Sp", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 581, "typeid": 218, "play": 996378, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/22e36b29b7b9c3789d30a7bfb9277fe92c5cc2a9.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "买了三个大榴莲，本来想把这种珍馐分给猫猫们吃，结果没有一个给面子的。于是我想到装在猫条里给它们，万万没想到，有的猫猫吃的还挺香啊！", "copyright": "1", "title": "把榴莲做成猫条给猫吃，猫的反应绝了！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1684573022, "length": "04:09", "video_review": 1200, "aid": 401258057, "bvid": "BV1Bo4y1F73j", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 640, "typeid": 218, "play": 1529372, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/cf28b6edb243827dbb7a890fc69937378291c03a.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "马赛克真是一种神奇的存在，有时候加上了之后反而变得更加有戏，可能这也是去往二次元的道路之一吧！", "copyright": "1", "title": "当猫遇上马赛克玻璃？！前方大量表情包出没哈哈哈", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1683968083, "length": "03:56", "video_review": 867, "aid": 613522268, "bvid": "BV12h4y1b7wa", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 268451968, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 445, "typeid": 218, "play": 524635, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/96948eb93ad9d1be576ae0010ed781f58d990dce.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "隐约记得家里还有两个要减肥的，不过现在已经顾不了那么多了，自从品尝过烤猪肘之后，就一直想复刻一次。这次厚着脸皮跟厨师取经，终于成功地复刻失败了，果然有的钱就是得让别人挣。", "copyright": "1", "title": "把德国烤猪肘复刻回家，猫猫吃了都说顶呱呱？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1682852400, "length": "07:05", "video_review": 957, "aid": 570524931, "bvid": "BV1Ez4y1Y7nM", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 404, "typeid": 218, "play": 485578, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/a30ec1095556f694b22f67fc81772466947aa943.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "如果没有小猫，我的房子会更加干净，我也能攒下更多的钱，但我的心，会空空的。", "copyright": "1", "title": "谁懂啊，家人们，这猫说它要跟我回家！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1682764588, "length": "04:00", "video_review": 778, "aid": 740610066, "bvid": "BV1mk4y177z8", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 268451968, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 469, "typeid": 218, "play": 528006, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/a49a00043371f52f4437c5a41a949df92a1cd924.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "减肥的事情一直是我们家每个人和猫关注的重点，众所周知，超重这个问题已经伴随我们很久了，为了能够保持身体健康，我们必须采取各种行动！当然我说的是猪猪，你们以为是谁？老父亲吗？反正无论如何，这次一定是最后一次了，不成功便成猪！加油！", "copyright": "1", "title": "为了吃减肥后的奖励零食，猫咪每天主动要求打开跑步机！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1682067600, "length": "06:27", "video_review": 990, "aid": 355337693, "bvid": "BV1vX4y1B7Hq", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 509, "typeid": 218, "play": 536151, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/307ac3d3dcdd97c961fb75ad8c593743e618ed33.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "上次在阳台做了露营地之后，感觉非常的棒！必须把露营要做的事情统统安排上！那么这期视频就从烧烤开始！", "copyright": "1", "title": "猫：“别催，马上烤好了”", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1680949168, "length": "06:59", "video_review": 1101, "aid": 312234445, "bvid": "BV1XN411c7mK", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 914, "typeid": 218, "play": 611944, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/e8bd47ab55c4ddf7f0935616a7162c5313c1d8da.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "这是一期关于爱的故事，我想把这份爱，传达给你们。但是我不是一个很会写文章的人，不会用华丽的词藻，也不会引经据典，更不能把一件小事讲出什么大道理。尽管如此，我也希望把身边的这些小故事，好好讲给你们听，希望你们能够从中感受到这份爱意～这不仅仅是分分对猪猪的爱，分分对我的爱，我对分分的爱，也是我对你们的爱～", "copyright": "1", "title": "有的猫，舔着舔着就长大（胖）了", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1680257900, "length": "03:57", "video_review": 995, "aid": 569344379, "bvid": "BV1yv4y1V7pj", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 268451968, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 578, "typeid": 218, "play": 779643, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/6ccb8b01fa16bd337f6260d0108681ec000c832c.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "带猫去露营这个心愿我想了好久了，但是想来想去都觉得要全部带上5只猫实在是太不现实了，终于今天实现了这个愿望～加上我又很喜欢这种及具包裹感的空间，就像是专属我的秘密基地一样，我可以在里面做任何我想做的事情～\n当然猫猫也是超级喜欢这次的改造，还有老父亲已经在和我一起抢帐篷了！感谢京东爸爸对这期节目的赞助播出，虽然是期广告，但是我是真的希望大家能够用拥有属于自己的独立空间～", "copyright": "1", "title": "猫：真的会谢，我妈竟然把露营搬到家里了？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1679397900, "length": "05:01", "video_review": 1291, "aid": 738808409, "bvid": "BV1pk4y1t7cM", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 531, "typeid": 218, "play": 863544, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/7fa65ec12672c753fb3e739bde069939eae94bde.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "买了根管子想试试让家里的猫变成柱柱猫！！！果然真的很可爱！！！原本想定制更细一点的，但是怕某只猫（我就不说是哪只了）钻不进去，就定制的比较粗，柱柱效果没有那么明显，但是也依旧好可爱！", "copyright": "1", "title": "再不放本喵出来就要生气辣！！！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1678938743, "length": "04:43", "video_review": 1120, "aid": 866040664, "bvid": "BV1L54y1T7P6", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 268451968, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 289, "typeid": 218, "play": 358068, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/b33efa777e729a718f8d3b97c6d32e18d1a70576.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "又到了给各位铲屎官排雷推荐的时间了，这次的几个玩具效果都还不错，尤其那个人猫两用的跳绳机器，非常适合大家给自己家的猫猫来用呀~", "copyright": "1", "title": "什么玩意能让猫直接开到180迈？！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1678438826, "length": "04:41", "video_review": 815, "aid": 525806846, "bvid": "BV1MM411x7ei", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 268451968, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 265, "typeid": 218, "play": 330180, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/d3fb0cba3ab4b07cc58060529d506f53b6d070f4.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "自从学习了猫咪行为学的课程，我发现很多我们对猫咪行为的认识都是错误的，作为一个铲屎官，想要真正在内心贴近猫猫，就要真正了解猫猫行为背后的含义~", "copyright": "1", "title": "五个突破你常识的猫咪行为学，不看可能你这辈子都还在误会它！", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1677320619, "length": "03:24", "video_review": 391, "aid": 310107817, "bvid": "BV1uA41127VP", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 574, "typeid": 218, "play": 654991, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/356ccd606a0c74c96311fce6adfb0c5fc841df46.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "目前检查的结果就是：中分是先天性的髋关节发育不完全，包裹性不好，导致会有疼痛的反应。医生的意思是再观察，如果后续还会再出现跛行的问题，可能就需要考虑手术方案了，不过也有可能后续几年都没有问题，只要不影响中分日常生活，就暂时不考虑手术方案。", "copyright": "1", "title": "猫猫我呀，腿腿痛痛，哭唧唧，需要哄哄～", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1676023200, "length": "04:53", "video_review": 812, "aid": 906709594, "bvid": "BV1jM4y1Q7ot", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}]}, "page": {"pn": 1, "ps": 50, "count": 347}, "episodic_button": {"text": "播放全部", "uri": "//www.bilibili.com/medialist/play/9008159?from=space"}, "is_risk": false, "gaia_res_type": 0, "gaia_data": null}}